## Optional: Sentry Integration

This worker includes optional Sentry error tracking. To enable:

1. Update your `context.ts` to extend `SharedHonoEnv`:
   ```typescript
   import type { SharedHonoEnv } from '@repo/hono-helpers'

   export type Env = SharedHonoEnv & {
     // add additional bindings here
   }
   ```

2. Add your Sentry DSN to `wrangler.jsonc`:
   ```jsonc
   "vars": {
     "SENTRY_DSN": "https://your-sentry-dsn@sentry.io/your-project-id"
   }
   ```

3. Wrap your handler with `instrumentHandler`:
   ```typescript
   import { instrumentHandler } from '@repo/hono-helpers'

   const handler: ExportedHandler<Env> = {
     fetch: (request, env, ctx) => {
       return new Response('hello, world!')
     }
   }

   export default instrumentHandler({ handler })
   ```
